{"tid":2394606,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年藏30枚煙霧彈囚38個月 官指一旦使用或令動盪局勢升溫","createTime":"2021-02-04T09:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:38:41.000Z","uid":56115,"like":5,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"957faa7f992c1e2c1b02802976e353793aa4ccc1","tid":2394606,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"警⽅前年8⽉在天⽔圍天瑞邨⼀個單位搜獲逾30枚土製煙霧彈，<span class=\"red\">拘捕一家三口</span>，最終僅當中一名23歲青年被控。青年早前承認管有炸藥及管有物品意圖摧毀財產兩罪，區域法院法官祁士偉今判刑指，案發時正值社會動盪，被告一旦使用涉案物品，或令局勢升溫，造成破壞；但考慮到該些物品<span class=\"red\">並非在示威現場搜獲</span>，以及被告並非打算使用它們解決人際糾紛等因素，判囚38個月。<br />\n<br />\n法官對管有炸藥罪採用24個月監禁作量刑起點，管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪則以45個月監禁作起點。被告承認兩罪，均可獲三分一減刑。惟法官指，兩罪所涉物品雖在同時同地搜出，但可產生不同效果，混合使用亦會加強效果，故此將管有炸藥罪的其中8個月刑期分期執行，最終判處被告監禁38個月。"},{"pid":"87dd9075f4870cd2ab5beceddace0cab422a4dc1","tid":2394606,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210204/ZQ6HOXF2JNGSBNPNRYY7X5YHF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210204%2FZQ6HOXF2JNGSBNPNRYY7X5YHF4%2F&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRJj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=50155386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210204%2FZQ6HOXF2JNGSBNPNRYY7X5YHF4%2F&h=d23832d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210204/ZQ6HOXF2JNGSBNPNRYY7X5YHF4/</a>"},{"pid":"07fba06a460164bb2898791844da44486380b4b4","tid":2394606,"uid":89683,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"屋企嘅漂白水 加醋 混合使用都會令局勢升溫啦<br />\n又唔拉嘅？"},{"pid":"3ba6a44620c783089b90ad63e8048cc0eeb28e1d","tid":2394606,"uid":278152,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"屌垃圾狗官"},{"pid":"124fd53459e4600d22e0010f3b6335319ceeb46b","tid":2394606,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse